rows.label: tlk70000119_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Just carry straight on down this road
and you'll come to Torigo Village.

rows.label: tlk70000119_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Try to stay on the road, though, OK?
There are some pretty scary monsters
around.

rows.label: tlk70000119_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Sometimes you get eager travelers
who stray too far from the road and
bump smack into 'em.

rows.label: tlk70000119_01_msg0004
tlk70000119_01_msg0005
rows.name:
I know adventuring can be rewarding,
but if you're like me and you value
your own life? Stick to the road!
